    dc:description "FIGURE 2–7. Cosmocerca acanthurum n. sp. (2) Male. (3) Female. (4) Excretory pore at level of oesophageal bulb, male. (5) Posterior end of male, lateral view. (6) Detail of posterior end of male, arragement of caudal papillae. (7) Posterior end of female. scale-bar: 0.1 mm." ;
